      <p facs='#facs_2_tr_1'>
	<lg>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_l'>at <placeName placeName='Home'><country>Scotland</country>Home</placeName>. Remember me to all my friends</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_3'>and acquaintances and believe me
          </l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_4'>Truely yours</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_5'>John Doe</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_6'>P.S.</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_7'>I would feel <strike-through>much</strike-through> indebted to you</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_8'>for the following articles.</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_9'>A few yards of blue flannel or</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_10'>Plaiding, Course stocking yarn.</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_11'>a few pairs of socks, stockings</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_12'>for the wife and children also</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_13'>apair of shoes for each of us</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_14'>likewise <hi rend='strikethrough:true;'>a quantity of</hi> striped</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_15'>shirting, stays for the children</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_16'>Jane and Alice would like dolls</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_17'>and beads.</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_18'>This <Language Scots='Yes' NZE='No'>letter is</Language> a copy of one written</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_19'>by John Doe to his sisters</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_20'>and brothers in Edinburgh</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_21'><country>Scotland</country> about his arrival in</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_l_148'>Otago N.Z. in January 1900</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_24'>for some unknown reason the</l>
	  <l facs='#facs_2_tr_1_tl_25'>letter had not been posted home</l>
	</lg>
      </p>
